hopobject.body: Not in at the moment cough syrup with codeine and promethazine uk In launching the Indiegogo campaign last month, Canonical revealed tentative specs for the so-called "superphone," including a 4.5-inch, 1,280-by-720 HD display, multi-core CPU, 4GB of RAM, and a massive 128GB of storage, plus an 8-megapixel rear camera and 2-megapixel front cam. With dual-LTE, dual-band 802.11n Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, NFC, and GPS, the device is akin to most mobile phones currently on the market.
